{"tid":2398091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Why 當年HKU咁多人反對醫學院用 李嘉誠明名？","createTime":"2021-02-07T04:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:51:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e23796d2f00d58884e267b5064835fb2a3d6200e","tid":2398091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofDhehf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofDhehf.jpg&h=3e6234c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港大將醫學院命名為「李嘉誠醫學院」，答謝李嘉誠捐出10億元，引發21名醫學院校友聯署反對，有份聯署的郭家麒醫生談起冠名風波仍憤憤不平，他批評大學「睇錢份上」，出賣逾130年歷史的醫學院的冠名權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180316/F62IB6WBP4FMMPBWL4SBHWJGZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180316%2FF62IB6WBP4FMMPBWL4SBHWJGZU%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJObY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=d88225d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180316%2FF62IB6WBP4FMMPBWL4SBHWJGZU%2F&h=2e46d0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180316/F62IB6WBP4FMMPBWL4SBHWJGZU/</a>"},{"pid":"5b5104912f6a5790d7a3eda321931aa44304be1b","tid":2398091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"藍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a173d1642c898a6de344cd1932441c166ed421","tid":2398091,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"郭家麒指，港大醫學院歷史悠久，校方毫無諮詢下突然以李嘉誠冠名醫學院，引起校友、教職員反對，「醫學院成立咗超過130年，第一代畢業生係孫中山先生，都係好崇高理想啲人。突然間有個爭議好大嘅香港商人，佢生意經營手法有好多非議，一個咁大非議嘅人，又同醫學界無乜關係，大學純粹睇錢去做（冠名）。」"},{"pid":"ddf93cb5f109f3db1f40d72a04ed81b44c71fbe7","tid":2398091,"uid":53062